reviewText: Can't understand very well. Hard to follow. It breaks up all the time and nothing makes sense due to the break up in audio. Would not recommend very disappointed!
v​ery good course to improve your English skills,  have proper strategies and be aware how to ace TOEFL test

I finished this course with the other two courses of the TOEFL Preparation Specialization within a week. Its very easy to digest and informative. My TOEFL Score just came back 109/120 and I'm very happy. I recommend taking notes throughout the course, paying attention to the readings and using the links they give you. As the course recommends, visit ETS's website and check out their videos/practice tests for a better understanding.
Undoubtedly, the course fully meets the proposed objectives. In addition, it provides all the tools for the best learning.
I learn a lot too many strategies and help things,i need to practice more and more to get it better
I found this course really easy to understand. Thanks to the instructor who prepared this great course for the TOEFL takers.
Excelentes tips en hacer mejoras para realizar el examen.
Este curso es  muy importante ya que deja un gran aprendizaje para poner en practica lo que se nos enseño en este curso para el día del examen.
Thank you for giving me the opportunity to take this course.
All the contents are detailed and clear!

V​ery helpful course to know strategies about TOEFL. Moreover, I would like to recommend all and sundry to join this course to get high score in iBT TOEFL exam. I'm very grateful to Coursera and University of California, Irvine to bring such a wondeful course to learners like me who want to fulfil their dreams to study abroad by taking admission in top ranked universities through TOEFL course. Once again I recommend this program should must be join by all future students for getting effective strategies about iBT TOEFL exam.
